altername_name: Hagane no Renkinjutsushi: Fullmetal Alchemist: Tasogare no Shoujo
name: Fullmetal Alchemist: Daughter of the Dusk
overview: Fullmetal Alchemist: Daughter of the Dusk (Tasogare no Shōjo) is an action game developed by Square Enix for Wii. Just like its predecessor Fullmetal Alchemist: Prince of the Dawn, it was never released outside Japan.
